The '''Colour Experience''' (formerly known as '''The Colour Museum''') is a [[visitor attraction]] and [[museum]] in [[Bradford]], [[West Yorkshire]], [[England]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://sdc.myzen.co.uk/museum/mus.htm |title=Colour Experience |publisher=Society of Dyers and Colourists, UK |accessdate=28 July 2011}}</ref>
